title: About Me
text: I am a computational neuroscience enthusiast with signal processing expertise. A passionate explorer of computational neuroscience methods, my diverse interests span from analyzing neural signals (spikes/fMRI/EEG/DTI) to developing cutting-edge dynamic models for neuroscientific applications. If you would like to collaborate with my explorations, please contact me.
